{"tid":1390550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賓州參議員Pat Toomey支持國會通過《香港人權及民主法》。他不是寫支持民主，而是支持自治。","createTime":"2019-07-31T07:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T16:45:11.000Z","uid":107060,"like":149,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"bee0f5c34ead30b42da52efe66176796a227560f","tid":1390550,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:24:28.000Z","msg":"陳雲：賓州參議員Pat Toomey支持國會通過《香港人權及民主法》。請留意，萬分留意，他不是寫支持民主，而是支持自治（in support of Hong Kong Autonomy）。在英文的政治修辭，自治的意思是什麼呢？請讀陳雲的《香港城邦論》，你就會知道我用自治這個政治修辭，令到國際社會可以名正言順支援香港。《香港城邦論》在華夏聖言出版社網購，速遞到付。"},{"pid":"c6efb6e0cf2d32bdabf91b8941fd52d713ea71a5","tid":1390550,"uid":78255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"希望冇人會用得著呢張卡片<br />\n<br />\n【8月2日集會】準備咗被補須知嘅卡片打算集會派<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dtBrdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dtBrdS</a>"},{"pid":"4f1341f8d377d3011a236b15c225acc6985febd7","tid":1390550,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5735359ceeb0a49b520b8665228105e83edde1ec","tid":1390550,"uid":176935,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:57:55.000Z","msg":"有無巴打一齊twitter/email呢位議員<br />\n果45個義士可唔可以申請美國政治庇護 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d08931d2cce32da406a799f453d76f0c0995d7e","tid":1390550,"uid":262264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:58:38.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"210773ac1a0eec8b2e3681b589919389e114296c","tid":1390550,"uid":82938,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:59:40.000Z","msg":"Washington, D.C.&nbsp;- U.S. Senator Pat Toomey (R-Pa.) is pursuing legislative action in&nbsp;support&nbsp;of protesters in Hong Kong who are fighting to preserve their democratic freedoms and independent legal system.<br />\nSenator Toomey is backing the bipartisan&nbsp;Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act&not; - introduced by Senator Marco Rubio (R-Fla.). The bill seeks to reaffirm the United States' commitment to democracy, human rights, and the rule of law for Hong Kongers at a time when China is seeking to erode Hong Kong's autonomy.<br />\n&quot;The protests in Hong Kong are grounded in the removal of an unpopular and unfair extradition bill,&quot;&nbsp;said Senator Toomey. &quot;However, the fight extends well beyond one piece of legislation. It extends to stopping the growth of Chinese authoritarianism, which poses a threat to basic human rights, including the right to free speech, the right to a fair trial, and the right to a genuinely representative government. This bipartisan legislation makes clear that the United States stands alongside the Hong Kong people in their struggle for freedom, and I urge all my colleagues to support this measure.&quot;<br />\n&quot;As over one million Hong Kongers take to the streets protesting amendments to the territory's extradition law, the U.S. must send a strong message that we stand with those peacefully advocating for freedom and the rule of law and against Beijing's growing interference in Hong Kong affairs,&quot;&nbsp;said Senator Rubio upon introduction. &quot;I am proud to re-introduce legislation that places the U.S. firmly on the side of human rights and democracy and against those who would erode the freedoms and autonomy guaranteed to the people of Hong Kong, freedoms that have made the city a prosperous global commercial hub governed by the rule of law.&quot;"},{"pid":"bcf1cc8196263fd95aa0f8d75144df5785b8cb79","tid":1390550,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6b1242c6a2e00ee09acdd9eeb75148bcc65dae","tid":1390550,"uid":202707,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:11:01.000Z","msg":"呢個禮拜多咗兩個國會議員支持香港人權及民主法案， 依家總共有19位國會議員支持， 距離推行仲差好遠， 大家有美國朋友麻煩叫佢哋幫手簽以下條link， 要有美國住址<a href=\"https://actionnetwork.org/letters/co-sponsor-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-of-2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Factionnetwork.org%2Fletters%2Fco-sponsor-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-of-2019&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=c6248633\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://actionnetwork.org/letters/co-sponsor-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-of-2019</a><br />\n呢個法案裏面有寫要香港喺2020年推行普選， 否則就會取消香港嘅獨特地位， 法案通過咗香港就有得救"},{"pid":"39df14557e23289dc8ac467eae435c99ad5ceeef","tid":1390550,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:12:21.000Z","msg":"阿賓州參議員，係就快啦，講左成2個月都黎"},{"pid":"476da284ce92bcd9d4a79db3c512692fc7c2d34f","tid":1390550,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4438f5b6630f5fb5b26b35b795754481f95ba8","tid":1390550,"uid":25468,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:13:36.000Z","msg":"就黎痾屎食飯都係陳雲發明"},{"pid":"4ab93f0c1aff396ca0c1933a093b000e78e42595","tid":1390550,"uid":207894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:13:38.000Z","msg":"幫推 文宣輿論戰線<br />\n<br />\n全民打手<br />\n自由閪吧 上線啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390411</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ff0471f4b64078168fb672b08751309f63ee20e9","tid":1390550,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36adfdafadbd0157ab452ea6afe340e6e7faef1a","tid":1390550,"